reviewText: I needed safe movies to show kids when visitors stayed with me for the the Christmas school break.  This fit the bill.  Kept the kids, ages 9 through 11, busy while we could keep one eye on them in another room.  Sometimes we would join them when things got exciting.  A couple of tear jerkers in there, but worth the while.
